hat=E2=80=99s what hedging is for. Certainly it is not a=C2=A0catastrophe=
=C2=A0for you that the price of nickel, which you produce, went up. You wer=
e making the nickel anyway, and you will deliver it at the agreed price.And=
 therefore if the market structure=C2=A0turns it into=C2=A0a catastrophe =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0if your brokers are bankrupted and the price of nickel futur=
