nd its defenders said?LME=E2=80=99s Chamberlain defended canceling the trad=
es. =E2=80=9COur fundamental responsibility is market stability,=E2=80=9D h=
e told Bloomberg TV. =E2=80=9CThe prices that were being seen during that A=
