isk, said Matt Chamberlain, LME=E2=80=99s chief executive.=E2=80=9COne of o=
ur key responsibilities is to serve the physical traders,=E2=80=9D he said.=
 =E2=80=9CIf we allowed the trades to stand, we would have to say that the =
