 =E2=80=A6Fir Tree is betting that its short wager could see a payday withi=
n 12 months and its thesis against Tether centers around the coin=E2=80=99s=
 roughly $24 billion in high-yield commercial paper, much of it the firm be=
lieves is tied to Chinese real estate developers. ...Genesis Global Trading=
 Inc., a crypto broker, has helped some asset managers put on Tether shorts=
 by lending the stablecoin itself or structuring put options. The company d=
oesn=E2=80=99t take a view on Tether and serves clients who are buyers of t=
he stablecoin.Like, Tether is a digital token that is supposed to be worth =
a dollar. (It is also=C2=A0the name of the entity, Tether Ltd., that issues=
 Tethers.)=C2=A0It is in fact worth a dollar: It trades on exchanges for ve=
ry close to a=C2=A0dollar, with very limited volatility. It is backed by a =
