nal customers can redeem Tethers for dollars, from Tether Ltd., one for one=
.You might believe =E2=80=94=C2=A0lots of people believe! =E2=80=94=C2=A0th=
at Tether is backed by bad commercial paper and that it will break. A big c=
ommercial-paper issuer will default, Tether (which keeps its holdings  very=
